# Woof Engineering Rules

## E2E Selector Convention

- Add `data-testid` only to elements that an automated test must target.
- Use the pattern `<page>-<element-purpose>` (for example: `boarding-new-booking-btn`).
- Prefer updating existing test IDs over introducing duplicates for the same action.
- Keep labels/placeholder text user-friendly; tests should rely on `data-testid` for stability.
- When a UI flow has both owner and pet variants, include entity context in the test ID suffix.
